.SH BUILT-IN COMMAND ALIASES
.TP
.B choose-session
Expands to
.BR "choose-tree -s" .
.TP
.B choose-window
Expands to
.BR "choose-tree -w" .
.SH NOTES
.B link-window
and
.B unlink-window
ship in the public CLI surface with tmux-style shared window links across
sessions, including linked-window format variables and hook context.
